marketing: Shell Corena S6 A is an extended oil life, top tier synthetic lubricant based on polyalkylene glycol (PAG) and pentaerythritol ester technology with next generation additives for rotary screw air compressors. The product helps provide extended oil drain intervals together with varnish formation protection benefits in higher temperature and pressure applications in challenging operations.
